{"tid":1943201,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「狗源」任天堂香港代理藍到發黑","createTime":"2020-03-25T13:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T06:34:33.000Z","uid":25825,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a05534ca1eb27957c93511fccb99a84d1a34964d","tid":1943201,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4uDWeaA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4uDWeaA.png&h=c6836476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依排出Animal Crossing 多咗人買Switch<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">主機推介去AEON / UNY / 豐澤買，港任話呢幾間係直接同佢地擺貨，寶源無錢落袋，或者直接Amazon 啦，唔好買行貨呀</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>買game 就買水貨/或者Nintendo e-shop買digital ，所有Nintendo switch 既game 都唔好買行貨</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大部份switch 既game無論封面乜嘢語言，入面都齊多國語言<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rCgkFJx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrCgkFJx.png&h=abf7d6eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">除咗老任外，以下幾間廠都係狗源代理（所以PS4都有影響），買digital或者水貨啦</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rQUeLa6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrQUeLa6.png&h=fe591a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面張圖無既廠就唔係狗源代理，行貨無問題（例如sega 同埋sony自己出既first party game)"},{"pid":"dcead1065f155aa4bd396b10bcc34009dfc9c0a8","tid":1943201,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:46:28.000Z","msg":"，"},{"pid":"d23af4a7e4f5da3a4596a14b0afd57a020ad629f","tid":1943201,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:46:41.000Z"